fields.name: data
fields.comment: can be a block/item id or other depending on the soundtype

fields.name: globalEvent
fields.comment: If true the sound is played across the server

fields.name: seed
fields.comment: First 8 bytes of the SHA-256 hash of the world's seed

fields.name: destId
fields.comment: The entity that is holding the leash, or -1 to clear the holder.

fields.name: containerId
fields.comment: The id of the window which was clicked. 0 for player inventory.

fields.name: action
fields.comment: Status of the digging (started, ongoing, broken).

fields.name: xxa
fields.comment: Positive for left strafe, negative for right
